suncertify.model
Interface ContractorModel

All Known Implementing Classes:
DBFileContractorModel
public interface ContractorModel

Defines a model for persisting contractor entities in a persistence storage. Contractor information are encapsulated in a bean of type Contractor.

This interface defines basic CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, and Delete) and a discard() to clean up this model when disposing it from use, clean up might be free resources and unlock records. The read operation is performed by a finder method find(suncertify.model.ContractorCriteria) which returns a list of Contractor instances which matches specific filtering criteria.

Author:
Mohammad S. Abdellatif
See Also:
Contractor, ContractorCriteria
